        3ms      8.0     48.0     0.118    7.67   6.69    33.8   [33.4, 51.6, 33.8, 39.9, 32.0]
        4ms      7.2     40.0     0.020    8.14   6.66    40.5   [36.7, 41.1, 40.5, 33.8, 55.5]
